{"tid":1685502,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"銀行網上繳款","createTime":"2019-10-31T14:46:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T16:58:23.000Z","uid":156913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d0ce53be8eeee1a68aac8517648133c4308be947","tid":1685502,"uid":156913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T14:46:09.000Z","msg":"無PPS, 所以緊銀行網上$1交錢法<br />\n小弟只有DBS, SCB同BEA<br />\n暫時網上繳款最密係BEA, 一星期一次<br />\n大家幫手check下自己間銀行, 有無一間可以set 重覆日日自動俾錢<br />\n如果有得日日自動, 係第一次手動set多D啫"},{"pid":"f946a0518e1c857a557bf3be376692eb1aa382f9","tid":1685502,"uid":156913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T15:42:46.000Z","msg":"有無人幫手check下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b3f6bc9123765b2b52fe949e622f93da97a455c","tid":1685502,"uid":127807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T15:44:16.000Z","msg":"有尐網上銀行既FORM可以記住以前輸入既野<br />\n或許有尐BROWSER可以記FORM<br />\n都幫到手"},{"pid":"dfc8eefe22044b52cb914d97b1d740e3db410256","tid":1685502,"uid":156767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T16:41:17.000Z","msg":"無每日，每月就有。<br />\n有macbook的話試下用macos原生program automator，可以用係銀行ebanking，我試過恒生ok，set左繳款template就用得，每日上限50次<br />\n<br />\nMac PPS 自動過數設定<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1653904\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1653904</a>"},{"pid":"7556a4e6e0e959903c59538128be0930f937bbbc","tid":1685502,"uid":178875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T16:43:26.000Z","msg":"好快又會被港共禁制令<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc211385530a7864e379f64d79c9f7a5efbddf90","tid":1685502,"uid":203616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7556a4e6e0e959903c59538128be0930f937bbbc","tid":1685502,"uid":178875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T16:43:26.000Z","msg":"好快又會被港共禁制令<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0